  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You manifest a pulse of thought, meant to inflict pain and disorient everyone near you.</p><p>All creatures of your choice, within range must make an Intelligence saving throw.</p><p>Success: Affected creature is able to resist this jutsu's effects.</p><p>Failure: Affected creature takes 3d4 psychic damage and is forced to move back 10 feet away from you.</p><p>Critical Failure: Affected creature takes 5d4 psychic damage and is forced to move back 25 feet away from you.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, damage by 1d4 and radius by 5 feet.</p>",
